Raffle of Alcohol
Raffle of Alcohol
page.curvetext:
In order to raffle alcohol the club must get a permit issued by the WSLCB.
In order to raffle alcohol the club must get a permit issued by the WSLCB.
page.enlisting:
▪ Ten dollars for a one time event. Twenty five dollars for an annual permit. ▪ Your club must fill out an application and submit it to the WSLCB in Olympia at ▪ Your club may not sell more then $5000 dollars worth of raffle tickets in a calendar ▪ No person under 21 can purchase raffle tickets when the prize is alcohol. ▪ All Washington State taxes must be paid. ▪ All alcohol must be purchased at retail (no club liquor) or by donation by private ▪ Only club members may purchase tickets or be awarded prizes. ▪ Ten dollars for a one time event.
